      <Readme>The CustomFields module contains four fields: 
  
  - Sortable Multilist with drag-and-drop functionality, 
  - Time Zones Droplist, 
  - Name-Value Droplist, 
  - Name-Value Droplists. 

These fields will improve the work of content editors and save their time.
	  
IMPORTANT!

After installation few references to scripts and css should be added to following layout “\sitecore\shell\Applications\Content Manager\Default.aspx”:
  &lt;script type="text/JavaScript" src="/js/jquery-ui.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;script type="text/JavaScript" src="/js/sortable-multilist.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;link href="/css/treelist.css" rel="stylesheet" /&gt;
</Readme>
